General Commands:
fields.value:
`.help`: Displays a Help Page
`.author`: To contact the Author
`.biegdich`: For a little Insider
`.clear [number]`: Clears text messages (1-100)

fields.name: Music Commands:
fields.value:
`.play [URL or TITEL]` or `.p`For playing music
`.skip` To skip to the next song in the queue
`.stop` or `.leave` or `.dc` Stops the Bot
